longBusinessSummary: Bakken Water Transfer Services, Inc., through its subsidiaries, engages in discovering, developing, and distributing green products and services. It intends to develop and market energy saving diode for standard light bulbs; and hydrogen assist cell for internal combustion engines. The company was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Minot, North Dakota.
